data.description: Welcome to 163 Overbrook Road, a prestigious residence nestled in the heart of Elyria. This home boasts a perfect blend of comfort and style, offering an ideal retreat for modern living. The well-designed floor plan features 5 bedrooms and 3 full and 3 half bathrooms providing ample space for both relaxation and entertainment. As you step inside, you will be greeted by marble flooring in the spacious foyer, a great room with fireplace that leads you into the gorgeous four-season room featuring lots of windows. The chefs eat-in kitchen is a true highlight, equipped with stainless appliances, quartz countertops, and an amazing entertainer's island. A formal dining room also features built-ins. There is a front office with fireplace and built ins.  Off the kitchen French doors lead you to a breezeway/gardening room. Finishing off the 1st floor is a large laundry room and the powder room. Upstairs are the generously sized bedrooms which all offer hardwood floors, a large bonus room above the garage and a small office.  We are conveniently located near medical facilities, major highways, shopping, restaurants, and schools! This home is a rare find, combining modern comforts with timeless appeal. Do not miss this once in a lifetime opportunity to live in a neighborhood where generations of family members have called home.
